ibis.deploy
Class Jungle

java.lang.Object
  ibis.deploy.Jungle

public class Jungle
extends java.lang.Object

Jungle containing resources. Basically just a HashMap with resource objects, and some functions for loading and saving jungles.

Author:
Niels Drost
